Twentynine Palms.title: Twentynine Palms
Twentynine Palms.byline: Twentynine Palms is a city of 26,000 (2021) in south central San Bernadino County in the California Desert located on the northern boundary of Joshua Tree National Park.

Tweed.title: Tweed
Tweed.byline: Tweed and the Land 'o Lakes region of Ontario cover a large, primarily-rural area north of Napanee-Belleville in Quinte-Northumberland.
